---
/**
 * Community Edition Banner
 * Displays at the top of every page to clarify this is the CE fork
 */
---

<div class="bg-brand-500 text-white py-2.5 px-4 text-center text-sm fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-[100] shadow-md">
  <p class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    This is <strong>OpenClaw Community Edition</strong> — a community-driven fork. 
    <span class="hidden sm:inline">Visit the official OpenClaw at</span>
    <a 
      href="https://openclaw.ai" 
      target="_blank" 
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="underline font-semibold hover:text-white/90 transition-colors ml-1"
    >
      openclaw.ai
    </a>
  </p>
</div>

<style>
  /* Push the header down to make room for the banner */
  :global(header) {
    margin-top: 2.75rem !important;
  }
</style>
